headline: Jacobs Appointed to UK's United Utilities Specialist Network Modeling Framework
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been appointed by United Utilities, one of the U.K.'s largest listed water companies, to deliver modeling support for water infrastructure through the asset management period (AMP8), which runs from 2025 to 2030.
